SAM: We have to look. Otherwise we have no leads
at all.

00:16:51.931 --> 00:16:53.769
LIAM: Let's head back to the Debt's Respite.

00:16:53.769 --> 00:16:56.456
LAURA: And get ready to leave, because we can't
hang around--

00:16:56.456 --> 00:16:58.826
TALIESIN: Talk to her employer so they know it
wasn't us.

00:16:58.826 --> 00:17:03.765
SAM: Wait, wait. Should we not scry from a
different place than the place we're staying at?

00:17:03.765 --> 00:17:05.787
TALIESIN: It's the place that she knows we are
already.

