MATT: She disguised her hand, she also a short
distance seemingly teleported or managed to break

00:18:38.695 --> 00:18:42.803
away from you guys and Trinket to make
her escape.

00:18:42.803 --> 00:18:48.411
TRAVIS: If she's anything like you, she might've
