MARISHA: If Trinket shoots himself in the ass...

00:19:38.959 --> 00:19:40.040
TALIESIN: It would be very funny, but--

00:19:40.040 --> 00:19:41.248
LAURA: He won't.

00:19:41.248 --> 00:19:43.351
TRAVIS: What do you want to do with it now? What's
the plan?

00:19:43.351 --> 00:19:46.257
TALIESIN: We're going to leave it with Trinket in
the other room for the moment, and we're going to

00:19:46.257 --> 00:19:50.700
discuss things. Leaving it under the bed with a
bear in the room.

