SAM: Shoot them with the gun.

00:20:02.244 --> 00:20:03.952
LAURA: (laughs) Shoot them with the gun.

00:20:03.952 --> 00:20:07.735
MATT: Licks the side of your face and gets back in
a restful period with the front of his paws and

00:20:07.735 --> 00:20:11.062
his head leaning over the edge of the bed, and the
