00:20:11.062 --> 00:20:13.123
LAURA: Don't you fall asleep.

00:20:13.123 --> 00:20:18.990
MATT: All right, so you guys head to one of the
other rooms, then?

00:20:18.990 --> 00:20:20.634
TRAVIS: Yeah.

00:20:20.634 --> 00:20:23.679
MATT: Okay. You guys close the door behind you.

00:20:23.679 --> 00:20:26.585
TRAVIS: Should I keep watch outside?

00:20:26.585 --> 00:20:29.263
LIAM: Yeah, that's a good idea.

00:20:29.263 --> 00:20:31.819
TRAVIS: I'll stand watch outside.

00:20:31.819 --> 00:20:34.320
MATT: And you do, Grog. This hallway is yours.

00:20:34.320 --> 00:20:39.231
LAURA: Don't you fall asleep, Grog.

00:20:39.231 --> 00:20:42.686
TRAVIS: (snoring)

