00:21:01.833 --> 00:21:05.003
LIAM: All right. Should we scry now, though?

00:21:05.003 --> 00:21:14.003
MARISHA: I have to study and then sleep on it,
because that's how my process works.

00:21:14.003 --> 00:21:17.534
