00:21:44.620 --> 00:21:46.406
TALIESIN: Bless you.

00:21:46.406 --> 00:21:50.494
MARISHA: What is it that I got? I have a little
ball--

00:21:50.494 --> 00:21:52.196
LAURA: The ball of seeing. The ball of scrying.

00:21:52.196 --> 00:21:54.630
MARISHA: Scrying Eye! I have the Scrying Eye.

00:21:54.630 --> 00:21:55.676
MATT: There you go.

