MARISHA: Do we want to do this here?

00:22:11.922 --> 00:22:13.390
LIAM: I think as soon as possible.

00:22:13.390 --> 00:22:17.761
TALIESIN: I think the question is, do we tell them
and see if we can enlist some help with this now

