00:22:30.995 --> 00:22:33.477
LAURA: We'll talk to... Treev?

00:22:33.477 --> 00:22:35.526
MARISHA: You guys figure it out, I'm going to
start scrying.

00:22:35.526 --> 00:22:42.003
TALIESIN: Figure out where she's going, what she's
doing, how many of them. All these things. I'm

00:22:42.003 --> 00:22:43.111
sorry.

00:22:43.111 --> 00:22:45.720
LAURA: Percy, we'll find her.

00:22:45.720 --> 00:22:48.071
TALIESIN: That's what I'm worried about.

00:22:48.071 --> 00:22:50.371
MATT: All right, so without the gun you don't get
the bonus from the item focus.

00:22:50.371 --> 00:22:51.356
MARISHA: Oh, fuck.

00:22:51.356 --> 00:22:53.232
MATT: But you also have the gun not in your
presence.

00:22:53.232 --> 00:22:57.687
MARISHA: Do we want to have the gun for this?
