00:22:57.687 --> 00:22:59.724
the other room, grab the gun, and scry.

00:22:59.724 --> 00:23:02.998
LAURA: I'm going to go sit with you while you
scry.

00:23:02.998 --> 00:23:05.920
MATT: Okay, you go into the room, and as you walk
toward the bed, Trinket growls at you.

00:23:05.920 --> 00:23:07.504
LAURA: Trinket.

00:23:07.504 --> 00:23:13.097
TALIESIN: I have another option. I have another
option. We still have her notes. We still have her notes.

00:23:13.097 --> 00:23:15.312
MARISHA: Does anything help?

00:23:15.312 --> 00:23:21.777
MATT: I mean, an object of which has some close
contact with the individual could help, yeah.

00:23:21.777 --> 00:23:22.850
MARISHA: Sure, whatever.

00:23:22.850 --> 00:23:24.741
TALIESIN: It is her diary notes of how to build my
gun.

