00:23:38.451 --> 00:23:42.116
MARISHA: I don't know, what do you think would be
better, her notes or?

00:23:42.116 --> 00:23:43.762
TALIESIN: Her notes. Let's be safe.

00:23:43.762 --> 00:23:45.448
MARISHA: Okay. I'm going to use her notes.

