LAURA: Do you want one? I have a bag.

00:24:05.759 --> 00:24:11.811
MATT: You know, I'll use the big one, then, that
Chris Perkins gave me.

00:24:11.811 --> 00:24:13.646
TRAVIS: And thus ends Vox Machina.

