00:25:02.240 --> 00:25:09.419
consciousness thrust through the clouds, white
clouds passing by, passing by, and then your

00:25:09.419 --> 00:25:13.730
vision comes back down through the clouds, only
instead of the desert, instead of the mountains,

00:25:13.730 --> 00:25:17.973
instead of anything in the nearby area, it's just
ocean. Just ocean.

00:25:17.973 --> 00:25:20.012
LAURA: She's fucking finding another one.

00:25:20.012 --> 00:25:22.641
MATT: Waves seem endless around you.

00:25:22.641 --> 00:25:24.035
MARISHA: Oh no.

