creaks, ropes swing, and you hear voices yell. A

00:25:40.763 --> 00:25:47.215
crew barely holding it together. Standing on the
deck, hooded, you see Ripley, calm, and looking

00:25:47.215 --> 00:25:53.036
out into the horizon. She smiles from beneath her
