00:26:05.165 --> 00:26:06.552
Six barrels.

00:26:06.552 --> 00:26:07.880
LIAM: Oh, snap.

00:26:07.880 --> 00:26:13.284
MATT: Lightning flashes once more in the distance,
followed by a very, very nearby crack of thunder.

