TALIESIN: No!

02:30:41.319 --> 02:30:43.791
SAM: 15.

02:30:43.791 --> 02:30:45.239
TRAVIS: 19.

02:30:45.239 --> 02:30:46.843
LAURA: 22.

02:30:46.843 --> 02:30:47.969
LIAM: 15.

02:30:47.969 --> 02:31:01.497
MATT: All right. Glancing about, mostly human
