MARISHA: We wanted her, right? Are we cool?

02:32:01.075 --> 02:32:04.723
TRAVIS: She dies.

02:32:04.723 --> 02:32:10.173
TALIESIN: Good for you. Excellent.

02:32:10.173 --> 02:32:12.959
MARISHA: What's her name? Did we ever get a name
