02:32:36.789 --> 02:32:37.902
legitimate.

02:32:37.902 --> 02:32:39.015
TALIESIN: And this is everybody?

02:32:39.015 --> 02:32:39.868
MATT: Yes.

02:32:39.868 --> 02:32:40.639
TRAVIS: Captain.

02:32:40.639 --> 02:32:41.590
MATT: "Yes?"

02:32:41.590 --> 02:32:46.777
TRAVIS: Who is it that's in charge of your
seaworthy navigations? The newest member of your

02:32:46.777 --> 02:32:48.190
crew you mentioned?

