MATT: "Well, that would be Teera. She's actually
been all about this ocean. Not necessarily by

02:32:54.722 --> 02:32:58.922
"skyship, but she knows the area as well, and has
since studied up and has become a very esteemed

02:32:58.922 --> 02:33:06.556
"member of our crew." He looks to her, and Teera's
