02:36:33.849 --> 02:36:37.247
LAURA: No, we'll stick with the Shrew.

02:36:37.247 --> 02:36:42.229
MATT: "I'll take you where I can."

02:36:42.229 --> 02:36:54.348
TRAVIS: The island of glass, is it called that
